Speaker 1: Thanks for speaking. How can I help you?

Speaker 2: Yeah. Hi. I was just looking to cancel my automatic—

Speaker 1: Okay, let me pull up your account one moment.

Speaker 2: Need to say Douglas, correct?

Speaker 1: Yes.

Speaker 2: All right, sir, so I do see you are a VIP here. I'm with the Viagra—

Speaker 1: Can I ask why you're cancelling? Do you mind if I ask you that?

Speaker 2: Just the cost and I'm not going through as quickly as the refill.

Speaker 1: Well, you can order as needed.

Speaker 2: You do not have to get it monthly or when you're not ready.

Speaker 1: I mean, am I able to just call whenever I need more?

Speaker 2: Yes, that's exactly what I just said, sir. You can order as needed.

Speaker 1: Uh-huh.

Speaker 2: Okay, so how that works for the next five months here we will not bill you or ship you anything.

Speaker 1: You're gonna have to call us in that time to receive your next order.

Speaker 2: All right.

Speaker 1: Sounds good.

Speaker 2: All right, amazing, sir. Yeah, that's all set up for you.

Speaker 1: All right, perfect. Well, thank you very much. Have a good day.

Speaker 2: You're welcome. You as well.

Speaker 1: All right.
